					<div class="indy-block-pricing-3 not-switchable"><div class="indy-heading-center"><h2 class="title-h2">Des formules adaptées à vos besoins</h2><p class="indy-heading-sub">La solution utilisée par + de 200 000 indépendants.&nbsp;Garantie sans frais cachés.</p></div><div class="main-wrapper  layout-row"><div class="pricing-card one-of-3 yearly simple-card  template-free no-features"><div class="flex-wrapper"><div class="card-header" style=""><span class="card-title title-h3" style="">Essentiel</span><div class="price-wrapper" style=""><div class="price"><span class="price-amount yearly choice-1">0</span><span class="price-amount monthly choice-1">0</span><div class="price-details"><div class="top"><span class="price-currency">€</span></div><div class="bottom"><span class="period">/mois</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="card-content "><div class="col col-1"><div class="price-wrapper large-card-only"><div class="price"><span class="price-amount yearly choice-1">0</span><span class="price-amount monthly choice-1">0</span><div class="price-details"><div class="top"><span class="price-currency">€</span></div><div class="bottom"><span class="period">/mois</span></div></div></div></div><p class="card-text">Les outils essentiels pour gérer votre activité simplement et gratuitement</p><a href="https://app.indy.fr/inscription/?signout=true" class="btn btn-primary addCookieDatatoURL ga-essentiel">Démarrer</a><span class="conditions yearly">Sans frais cachés</span><span class="conditions monthly">Sans frais cachés</span></div><div class="col col-2"></div></div></div></div><div class="pricing-card one-of-3 yearly simple-card  template-plus no-features"><div class="flex-wrapper"><div class="card-header" style=""><span class="card-title title-h3" style="">Plus</span><div class="price-wrapper" style=""><span class="before-amount choice-1">Dès</span><div class="price"><span class="price-amount yearly choice-1">9</span><span class="price-amount monthly choice-1"></span><div class="price-details"><div class="top"><span class="price-currency">€</span></div><div class="bottom"><span class="period">/mois</span><span class="price-after choice-1">HT</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="card-content "><div class="col col-1"><div class="price-wrapper large-card-only"><span class="before-amount choice-1">Dès</span><div class="price"><span class="price-amount yearly choice-1">9</span><span class="price-amount monthly choice-1"></span><div class="price-details"><div class="top"><span class="price-currency">€</span></div><div class="bottom"><span class="period">/mois</span><span class="price-after choice-1">HT</span></div></div></div></div><p class="card-text">Toutes les fonctionnalités avancées pour gagner du temps et piloter votre activité</p><a href="https://app.indy.fr/inscription/?signout=true" class="btn btn-primary addCookieDatatoURL ga-plus">Démarrer</a><span class="conditions yearly">30 jours satisfait ou remboursé</span><span class="conditions monthly">Sans engagement</span></div><div class="col col-2"></div></div></div></div><div class="pricing-card one-of-3 yearly simple-card  template-premium no-features"><div class="flex-wrapper"><div class="card-header" style=""><span class="card-title title-h3" style="">Premium</span><div class="price-wrapper" style=""><span class="before-amount choice-1">Dès</span><div class="price"><span class="price-amount yearly choice-1">12</span><span class="price-amount monthly choice-1"></span><div class="price-details"><div class="top"><span class="price-currency">€</span></div><div class="bottom"><span class="period">/mois</span><span class="price-after choice-1">HT</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="card-content "><div class="col col-1"><div class="price-wrapper large-card-only"><span class="before-amount choice-1">Dès</span><div class="price"><span class="price-amount yearly choice-1">12</span><span class="price-amount monthly choice-1"></span><div class="price-details"><div class="top"><span class="price-currency">€</span></div><div class="bottom"><span class="period">/mois</span><span class="price-after choice-1">HT</span></div></div></div></div><p class="card-text">Toutes vos déclarations fiscales, avec l’accompagnement de nos spécialistes</p><a href="https://app.indy.fr/inscription/?signout=true" class="btn btn-primary addCookieDatatoURL ga-premium">Démarrer</a><span class="conditions yearly">30 jours satisfait ou remboursé</span><span class="conditions monthly">Sans engagement</span></div><div class="col col-2"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bottom-wrapper"><a href="https://www.indy.fr/prix" class="btn btn-secondary">Découvrir nos formules</a></div></div>				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-14d39aa elementor-widget elementor-widget-indy-premium-banner" data-id="14d39aa" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="indy-premium-banner.default">
					<div class="indy-premium-banner-widget small"><div class="main-wrapper"><div class="img-wrapper right"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.indy.fr/wp-content/uploads/img-fusee-indy.png" alt="" class="desktop-only" width="298" height="298"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.indy.fr/wp-content/uploads/img-fusee-indy.png" alt="" class="mobile-only" width="298" height="298"></div><div class="content-wrapper"><h2 class="title-h2">Votre création d'entreprise offerte avec Indy</h2><p class="text">Nos spécialistes en création d’entreprise vous accompagnent gratuitement.</p><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="if (!window.__cfRLUnblockHandlers) return false; Calendly.initPopupWidget({url: &#039;https://calendly.com/d/dry-txn-5fp?primary_color=FA5D89&amp;background_color=FFF9F0&#039;});return false;" class="btn btn-primary gaevent-demo addCookieDatatoCalendlyURL" data-cf-modified-ee0afe089e276da858c411dd-="">Prendre rendez-vous</a></div></div></div>				</div>
